race.comment: BLUE ALLURE (4) just missed the placings in town at the latest effort and should find this assignment a touch easier. Gets the services of Thompson in the irons to navigate from the wide draw and rates a leading contender in this line-up. LONE ARTIST (2) resumes here but has placed two of three when fresh and has revved up for this with a recent trial placing. Looms as the main danger. BREEZIN' (6) is a consistent commodity who has hit the top-four in all six runs this preparation. Yet to miss a drum in four spins around this circuit and is a must for the multiples. READY TO SCHIPP (1) is a second-up winner in the past and gets some weight off with the 1.5kg claim. Don't dismiss lightly. JOY A PLENTY (3) rounds out the selections.
